<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v9" title="Q19_v9" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En un problema de perímetro se indica: "Un rectángulo tiene dos lados de longitud 4√3 m y dos lados de longitud 5 m. Un estudiante escribió el perímetro como P = 2·4√3 + 10". Se desea simplificar solo el término
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa correctamente este término escrito en forma simplificada?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>12</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, esta opción no representa correctamente el término.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se simplifica multiplicando los factores numéricos: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, la forma simplificada correcta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>12</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero el término dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, esta opción no es correcta.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, el término dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, que no es igual a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Esta opción no representa correctamente la simplificación pedida.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar el término que se debe simplificar</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado pide simplificar solamente:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los factores numéricos</strong></p>
            <p>Primero se multiplican los números <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Escribir el resultado junto a la raíz</strong></p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión obtenida es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Esa expresión corresponde a la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión simplificada correcta del término dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>